    <p>
      It is at this point that the NOI Statement for the Top Slice can be
      calculated, subtracting each of the Bottom Slice (traditional office)
      lines from the Property Projections (serviced office). This will provide
      us with an NOI of <b>$1,263</b> for the Top Slice.
    </p>
