      contribute <b>$12,625</b> in value for a total property value of
      <b>$38,750</b>.
    </p>
    <p>
      This would imply a Capitalization Rate of <b>7.30%</b> for the property
      utilizing serviced office leasing, which is calculated by dividing the NOI
      for the property by the Valuation.
    </p>
